{"title":["Stratego/Xt 0.17. A Language And Toolset For Program Transformation","stratego xt 0 17 a language and toolset for program transformation"],"author":[{"rawString":"martin bravenboer"},{"rawString":"karl trygve kalleberg"},{"rawString":"rob vermaas"},{"rawString":"eelco visser"}],"abstract":["Stratego/XT is a language and toolset for program transformation. The Stratego provides rewrite rules expressing basic transformations, programmable rewriting strategies controlling the application of rules, concrete syntax patterns in object language, dynamic context-sensitive thus supporting development transformation components at high level abstraction. XT offers collection flexible, reusable components, tools generating such from declarative specifications. Complete systems are composed these components. This paper gives an overview 0.17, including description tools; discussion implementation techniques software engineering process; applications built with Stratego/XT."],"numberOfReferences":[63,56],"numberOfCitations":[277,120,0],"year":2008,"publisher":["Elsevier North-Holland, Inc.","Elsevier BV"],"type":"journal-article","pdf":["http://martin.bravenboer.name/docs/est08.pdf","https://core.ac.uk/display/21124102","https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1016/j.scico.2007.11.003","https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.scico.2007.11.003","https://www.narcis.nl/publication/RecordID/oai%3Atudelft.nl%3Auuid%3Aff9544b2-7bee-42d7-b4ec-5425eeabcba3","https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0167642308000452","http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.scico.2007.11.003","https://doi.org/10.1016/j.scico.2007.11.003","https://api.elsevier.com/content/article/PII:S0167642308000452?httpAccept=text/xml","https://api.elsevier.com/content/article/PII:S0167642308000452?httpAccept=text/plain"],"uniqueId":[{"type":"DOI","value":"10.1016/J.SCICO.2007.11.003"},{"type":"MicrosoftAcademic","value":2125872407},{"type":"DOI","value":"10.1016/j.scico.2007.11.003"},{"type":"ISSN","value":["0167-6423"]},{"type":"ISB